{"tid":865860,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"屯門居屋連環劈！兆康540萬變440萬　美樂1個月內減70萬","createTime":"2018-10-17T12:05:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-18T00:56:37.000Z","uid":83582,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"720815e4232f53a4804c0fa8cd93862cce92748c","tid":865860,"uid":83582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T12:05:14.000Z","msg":"10月17日(三) 18:40<br />\n<br />\n屯門已補價自由市場居屋連環減價。益祥林英傑表示，兆康苑G座中層戶，實用面積449方呎，8月開價540萬元，原業主有套現需要，減價100萬元後，以440萬元沽貨，呎價僅約9,800元，同類單位9月成交價達540萬元，期內賣平18.5%。<br />\n<br />\n該行黃慶德亦稱，同區美樂花園9座高層D室，實用面積589方呎，9月底叫價655萬元，減五口價後，以585萬元轉手，呎價9,932元。據了解，同類單位市價可達約600萬元。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20181017/photo/bkn-20181017184025961-1017_00842_001_01b.jpg?20181017184624\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20181017%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181017184025961-1017_00842_001_01b.jpg%3F20181017184624&h=8fff991a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20181017/bkn-20181017184025961-1017_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20181017%2Fbkn-20181017184025961-1017_00842_001.html&d=EuBWzc3B4ccnLZoBWH7bVL%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=0e078c51\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20181017/bkn-20181017184025961-1017_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"c79238a3d3bc690c6545cb29a03728fe889ca65b","tid":865860,"uid":75877,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T12:06:14.000Z","msg":"原業主有套現需要<br />\n<br />\n個別事件<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6078e884bc727f8bdbe78ad0f5acb1b66dc7f9e7","tid":865860,"uid":163842,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T12:06:32.000Z","msg":"TM唔計啦"},{"pid":"ba7ab65f8d4beabc2c3e732e676e526016ddbf3b","tid":865860,"uid":159798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-17T12:06:45.000Z",